title: HelloHero: One-Pot Chicken & Veggie Penne with Parsley
description: Something magical happens when you combine this decadent creamy sauce with chicken and veggies. Watch the sparks fly as
this pasta dish is transformed before your very eyes into the most delicious bowl in all the land!

*We’ve replaced the fusilli in this recipe with penne due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your
recipe card!*
